   <m:mrow>
    <m:mn>238</m:mn></m:mrow>
  </m:msup>
  <m:mtext>U</m:mtext></m:mrow>
</m:math> . At the same time that the uranium shell reflects the neutrons back into the fuel to enhance its fusion, the fast-moving neutrons cause the plentiful and inexpensive  <m:math>
